live, /health/ready)\n500: - [ ] Invocation routes registered with GET and POST\n501: - [ ] Middleware chain applied (concurrency, logging, recovery)\n502: - [ ] SessionManager interface defined\n503: - [ ] GetSandboxBySession resolves or creates sessions\n504: - [ ] createSandbox POST to Workload Manager\n505: - [ ] K8s SA token added for in-cluster auth\n506: - [ ] ReverseProxy with custom Director\n507: - [ ] Director normalizes path and injects JWT\n508: - [ ] ModifyResponse adds session header\n509: - [ ] ErrorHandler maps errors to HTTP codes\n510: - [ ] JWTManager with RSA key generation\n511: - [ ] GenerateToken with RS256, 5m expiration\n512: - [ ] TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret handles creation/loading\n513: - [ ] AlreadyExists handled for concurrent routers\n514: - [ ] concurrencyLimitMiddleware with semaphore\n515: - [ ] 429 returned when overloaded\n516: - [ ] handleHealthLive returns 200\n517: - [ ] handleHealthReady checks sessionManager\n518: - [ ] handleInvoke proxies to sandbox\n519: - [ ] Activity timestamp updated twice\n520: - [ ] Error types implement APIStatus\n521: - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL required\n522: - [ ] AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE with default\n523: - [ ] Constants defined (rsaKeySize, jwtExpiration, IdentitySecretName)\n524: - [ ] Unit tests for all components\n525: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n526: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n527: - [ ] Unit tests pass with >80% coverage\n528: - [ ] No race conditions detected\n529: \n530: ---\n531: \n532: ## Files Modified/Created\n533: \n534: | File | Status | Description |\n535: |------|--------|-------------|\n536: | `pkg/router/errors.go` | Pending | Error types with APIStatus interface |\n537: | `pkg/router/errors_test.go` | Pending | Error types unit tests |\n538: | `pkg/router/config.go` | Pending | Config struct and DefaultConfig |\n539: | `pkg/router/config_test.go` | Pending | Config unit tests |\n540: | `pkg/router/store.go` | Pending | Store interface definition (or impor